title: Horoscopes: Catherine Tennant looks at the week ahead
text: Virgo Aug 24-Sep 23 From Monday, when the Sun moves into Virgo, you will be able to sweep obstacles aside, so do not let your doubts about a current project make you overcautious. Your financial situation takes an upward turn from Friday. Let events unfold and make no hard and fast decisions yet.
